<DOCID> 083653 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 29, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition Correction Appended 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 2; Column 2; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
