</P>
<P>
 Also, there will be food areas, a vintage guitar show, kids areas and 
blues-oriented arts and crafts. $10 to $15 per day. $25 VIP weekend passes 
available only in advance. For information, call (714) 645-1999. For tickets, 
call Ticketmaster at (714) 740-2000. 
</P>
