 SAN MARINO: Three burglars tied up a 40-year-old San Marino woman Tuesday 
morning when she returned to her home on Shakespeare Drive during a burglary. 
The woman escaped unharmed shortly afterward, police said. The burglars took 
$15,000 worth of stereo equipment and other items. 
</P>
