EAST VALLEY FOCUS: SYLMAR; SEXUAL HARASSMENT TO BE FOCUS OF TALK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JEFF SCHNAUFER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Is it verbal abuse or sexual harassment? 
</P>
<P>
 How to identify the difference will be the subject of a free talk at Mission 
College from noon to 1:30 p.m. Oct. 12. 
</P>
<P>
