<TEXT>
<P>
 The City Council extended a ban on fortunetellers for 10 months to give 
officials more time to study how seers should be regulated. 
</P>
<P>
 The council had approved a 45-day ban in August after Whittier resident 
Barbara Adams sought to open a fortunetelling business in the city. 
</P>
<P>
 Santa Fe Springs has no fortunetellers and they are not covered in city zoning 
laws. City officials said they were caught off guard and want to study how 
fortunetellers can affect an area. JOHN D. WAGNER 
