Virginia (1-4) 6-34, Virginia Tech Missouri 6. New Mexico (0-4) 47-49, BYU 
Colorado State 7. SMU (1-3) 7-35, Texas Tech North Carolina 8. UTEP (1-3) 7-47, 
Air Force Hawaii 9. Arizona State (1-3) 21-25, Cal Stanford 10. Indiana (3-1) 
