<P>
PREP ROUNDUP; WOODBRIDGE RALLIES PAST MATER DEI IN TENNIS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Woodbridge, the fourth-ranked girls' tennis team in Orange County, rallied to 
beat No. 9 Mater Dei, 10-8, Wednesday in a nonleague match at Woodbridge. 
</P>
<P>
 The Warriors (8-1) trailed, 4-2, after the first round. Woodbridge's No. 2 
