 Dana Hills 10, Corona del Mar 8 -- Nina Vaughan swept in singles, 6-4, 6-0, 
6-2, for No. 10 Corona del Mar, but Lara Spica, Summer Tantee and Karlie Noyes 
each won two of three sets for visiting Dana Hills (5-2), ranked third in the 
county. 
